Text: A penis (or a dick) is a man’s sexual organ. It’s part of his reproductive system and it’s  made of layers of spongy tissue which fills with blood when it gets hard. Sometimes parents choose to have a doctor remove the foreskin around the top of a baby boy's penis just after he's born - called circumcising.
